ge" class="pyro-image alignment-none" src="{{ url:site }}files/large/85" /></p>\n	<p>\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<p>\n		<strong>Finalists will be:</strong></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Announced at a special ceremony in Silicon Valley on March 7, 2013.</li>\n		<li>\n			Invited to display their solution at the all-day conference at NASA Ames Research Center in Silicon Valley on May 23, 2013.</li>\n		<li>\n			Receiving discounted admission to the May 23, 2013 event.</li>\n		<li>\n			Solutions will be published on the EcoCloud website and widely publicized through both traditional and social media channels.</li>\n	</ul>\n	<p>\n		<strong>Best solutions from the following categories will be selected and recognized:</strong></p>\n	<div class="well well-large">\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n				OVERALL BEST SOLUTION</li>\n			<li>\n				BEST CATEGORY SOLUTIONS (Resources, Human Systems, Enterprise, Regional, Industry, Earth Systems)</li>\n			<li>\n				BEST SYSTEM OF SOLUTIONS (3 or more solutions that form a planetary system)</li>\n			<li>\n				BEST SOLUTION FOR INDIVIDUAL IMPACT</li>\n			<li>\n				YOUNG INNOVATOR CATEGORY (aged 30 and under)</li>\n			<li>\n				NON-PROFIT CATEGORY</li>\n			<li>\n				CORPORATE CATEGORY</li>\n			<li>\n				RESEARCH CATEGORY</li>\n			<li>\n				"SEASONED" INNOVATOR CATEGORY (independent professionals, aged 30 and over)</li>\n		</ul>\n	</div>\n	<p>\n		<strong>Winners will be:</strong></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Announced at the WEST Summit/Showcase on May 23, 2013.</li>\n		<li>\n			Each winner will get Promotional/Marketing opportunities via premier placement of their solutions on the EcoCloud Marketplace.</li>\n	</ul>\n	<p>\n		<strong>This promotion will:</strong></p>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n			Bring VISIBILITY to their solution(s).</li>\n		<li>\n			Accelerate MARKET ADOPTION and progress towards solving global sustainablity.</li>\n		<li>\n			Give opportunities to INTERACT with potential innovators and customers.</li>\n	</ul>\n</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', '', 'wysiwyg-advanced', 1, 'default'),
