(1700, 'default', 77, '<p>\n	<span class="font-size-2">Are you on a Green Team or do you want to start one?&nbsp; You are not alone.&nbsp; Here are some resources to give you ideas and encouragement, get you started, and help you succeed:</span></p>\n<br />\n<h3>\n	Why Green Teams are good, how they work, and how to get one started:</h3>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.greenbiz.com/news/2008/06/07/corporate-green-teams-sustainable-business-bottom">Corporate Green Teams: Sustainable Business from the Bottom Up</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.p2ad.org/toolkit/guidebook_3.html">Forming the Green Team: Advice on forming a green team in an office or building</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?fuseaction=bygtw.showSplash">Start a Green Team</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.greenbiz.com/news/2008/10/12/leading-middle-power-green-champion">Leading from the Middle: The Power of Green Champions</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.sustainablesv.org/sites/default/files/dms/architecture-green-teams.pdf">The Architecture of Green Teams</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.greenbiz.com/research/report/2009/12/03/green-teams-engaging-employees-sustainability">Green Teams: Engaging Employees in Sustainability. Article by Deborah Fleischer</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.greenwala.com/community/blogs/all/786-Top-10-Tips-to-Green-Your-Workplace?f=true">Top 10 Tips to Green Your Workplace. Article by Justine Burt</a></span></li>\n	<li>\n		<span class="font-size-2"><a href="http://www.sustainablesv.org/sites/default/files/dms/bay-area-green-teams-top-challenges-2009.xls">Bay Area Green Teams Top Challenges 2009</a> Notes from Green Team Leaders Meeting, Sept 2009. Top challenges facing Green Team Leaders among