(10, 'Garden Creations JB5629 Solar-Powered LED Accent Light', 'live', 'From the Manufacturer\r\nNo wiring or electricity is required to install these Garden Creations solar-powered LED accent lights. They soak up the sun''s energy by day and shine brightly at night. The white LED lights illuminate walks, gardens, and patios. This set includes eight lights, each of which measures 4.25 inches by 4.25 inches by 13.5 inches.', '', '', NULL, 0, 0, 5, 4, 1353537461, 0),
(12, 'Energy Periscope TM', 'live', 'Building on more than a decade of front-line experience working with solar & renewable energy professionals, EnergyPeriscopeTM is designed to speed up and enhance the sales process. Easily crunch the numbers, generate professional sales proposal materials, and manage your sales activities. EnergyPeriscopeTM helps you focus on what really counts: identifying your customers needs, designing smart solutions, and getting new business on the books.', 'http://www.energyperiscope.com/', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353537723, 0),
(13, 'Solar-Estimate CPFTools', 'live', 'CPFTools is a trademark of Clean Power Finance Inc. This software was originally developed by Energy Matters LLC the company behind Solar-Estimate.org.', 'http://www.solar-estimate.org/?page=solar-software', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353537848, 0),
(14, 'Green Light for Sustainability Urban Development', 'live', 'http://www.siemens.com/entry/cc/en/urbanization.htm\r\nOSRAM has been producing innovative lighting solutions for professional applications. From general lighting, electronic control gears and lighting components to opto semiconductors & LEDs, display optic lighting, and automotive lighting OSRAM provides information, software and suggestions for lighting.', 'http://www.siemens.com/entry/cc/en/urbanization.htm', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353538018, 1353539025),
(15, 'Liquid Phase Carbon Treatment Equipment and Systems', 'live', 'Siemens Water Technologies provides activated carbon adsorbers and systems to filter and remove contaminants from liquid streams for industrial, municipal or commercial applications. Our systems are permanent, hard-piped as well as options for removable adsorber equipmen', 'http://www.water.siemens.com/en/products/activated_carbon/liquid_phase_carbon_treatment_equipment/Pages/default.aspx', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353538175, 1353538826),
(16, 'Green Building Materials', 'live', 'The concept of sustainable building incorporates and integrates a variety of strategies during the design, construction and operation of building projects. The use of green building materials and products represents one important strategy in the design of a building.\r\n\r\nGreen building materials offer specific benefits to the building owner and building occupants:\r\n\r\nReduced maintenance/replacement costs over the life of the building.\r\nEnergy conservation.\r\nImproved occupant health and productivity.\r\nLower costs associated with changing space configurations.\r\nGreater design flexibility.', 'http://www.calrecycle.ca.gov/greenbuilding/materials/', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353538353, 1354076452),
(17, '150 Best Eco House Ideas [Hardcover]', 'live', 'Featuring an extensive collection of full-color photographs, 150 Best Eco House Ideas features eco-friendly house designs created by internationally renowned architects and designers who have achieved practical, innovative, and stunning solutions adapted to the specific needs and tastes of their clients. Included here are the latest innovations in sustainable home design, including solar paneling, wind energy systems, environmentally-friendly heating and cooling solutions, thermal glazing, and trombe walls.\r\n\r\n150 Best Eco House Ideas covering the diversity of current trends in sustainable home design, and is both the perfect resource for designers, interior decorators, and architects, as well an inspirational sourcebook for all homeowners interested in creating warm and inviting homes that cause only a fraction of the environmental impact of those created using conventional building methods.', 'http://www.amazon.com/150-Best-Eco-House-Ideas/dp/006196879X/ref=sr_1_11?ie=UTF8&qid=1353538574&sr=8-11&keywords=eco+friendly+home', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353538644, 0),
(18, 'Premium no-VOC interior and exterior paints', 'live', 'Portland, Oregon-based Yolo Colorhouse offers premium no-VOC interior and exterior paints with a user-friendly color palette. One gallon of Semi-Gloss Interior Paint is $35 from Home Depot.', 'http://www.yolocolorhouse.com/#4', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353538772, 1353538846),
(19, '2012 Ford Fusion Hybrid', 'live', 'The 2012 Ford Fusion Hybrid ranks 1 out of 19 Affordable Midsize Cars. This ranking is based on our analysis of 36 published reviews and test drives of the Ford Fusion Hybrid, and our analysis of reliability and safety data.\r\n\r\nThe 2012 Ford Fusion Hybrid impressive performance, high-tech interior and good fuel economy make it a reviewer favorite.', 'http://usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/cars-trucks/rankings/Hybrid-Cars/', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353539002, 1354076502),
(20, 'Voltaic Solar Chargers', 'live', 'The Voltaic solar chargers are mobile power generators, designed to charge your devices using solar energy without tying you to a power outlet, which makes them perfect for traveling.\r\n\r\nAll the bags come with the battery pack and a set of 9 standard adapters for common cell phones and other devices.\r\n\r\nInside each charger is a Lithium-ion battery pack.', 'http://store.sundancesolar.com/vosobabada.html', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353539095, 0),
(21, 'Voltaic Solar Backpacks', 'live', 'The Voltaic solar backpacks are mobile power generators, designed to charge your devices using solar energy without tying you to a power outlet, which makes them perfect for traveling.\r\n\r\nAll the bags come with the battery pack and a set of 9 standard adapters for common cell phones and other devices.', 'http://store.sundancesolar.com/vosobabada.html', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353539095, 0),
(22, 'Voltaic Solar Bags', 'live', 'The Voltaic solar bags are mobile power generators, designed to charge your devices using solar energy without tying you to a power outlet, which makes them perfect for traveling.\r\n\r\nAll the bags come with the battery pack and a set of 9 standard adapters for common cell phones and other devices.\r\n\r\nInside each bag is a Lithium-ion battery pack that stores any surplus power.', 'http://store.sundancesolar.com/vosobabada.html', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353539096, 0),
(23, 'EBMUD wastewater treatment', 'live', 'EBMUD provides wastewater treatment services for Alameda, Albany, Berkeley, El Cerrito, Emeryville, Kensington, Oakland, Piedmont, and parts of Richmond.  The wastewater treatment charges are detailed below and are based on the type of customer, and on wastewater strength and volume.', 'http://www.ebmud.com/our-water/wastewater-treatment/wastewater-treatment-programs/wastewater-rates-charges-and-fees', '', NULL, 0, 0, 1, 4, 1353539341, 1354076525),
(24, 'California Materials Exchange (CalMAX) Portal', 'live', 'CalRecycle''s CalMAX portal connects businesses, organizations, manufacturers, schools, and individuals with the most effective online resources for exchanging materials. One business'' trash is another business'' treasure. By reusing materials, we conserve energy, resources, and landfill space, while reducing disposal, green house gas emissions, and purchasing costs. CalRecycle no longer lists individual materials available for exchange because the links below provide better online options. Please use one or more of the following resources to list or find materials. Thank you for your continuing commitment to reuse!', 'http://www.calrecycle.ca.gov/calmax/', '', NULL, 0, 0, 9, 4, 1353539444, 1354076568);
